CARD: Roleplay business card

Syntax: card [set <text>|show <player>|clear]

Store a short business card on your character for roleplay
introductions.

  card              show your card to everyone in the room
  card set <text>   set or replace your card (240 char max)
  card show <name>  hand your card privately to one player
  card clear        remove your card

Cards are saved on your character file.

SEE ALSO: introduce, biography, who
